title: Red Cake Pool Dissolve
story: dungeo
description: ADR-227 Phase 2 - throwing the red-icing cake (RDICE "Evaporate") in the Pool Room dissolves the pool and reveals the spices via the CakeThrowingInterceptor

---

# Setup - light + teleport to Tea Room
> gdt
[OK: contains "GDT ready"]

> tk brass lantern
[OK: contains "Taken"]

> ex
[OK: contains "Returning"]

> turn on lantern
[OK: contains "switches on"]

> gdt
[OK: contains "GDT ready"]

> ah Tea Room
[OK: contains "Teleported"]

> ex
[OK: contains "Returning"]

# Take the red cake, shrink via eat-me cake, go to Pool Room
> take red cake
[OK: contains "Taken"]

> eat eat-me cake
[OK: contains "smaller"]

> east
[OK: contains "Pool Room"]

# Spices hidden under the pool before the throw
> take tin
[OK: contains "see"]

# Throw the red cake at the pool -- dissolves it, reveals spices
> throw red cake at pool
[OK: contains "dissolve"]
[EVENT: false, type="if.event.player.died"]

# Spices now takeable
> take tin
[OK: contains "Taken"]
